---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="Kaleb | Dunn-Keaney"
    description="Systems, judgment, work, and writing from Kaleb Dunn."
    image="/images/kaleb-portrait.jpg"
    mainClass="kaleb-main"
>
    <div class="kaleb-page">
        <section class="kaleb-hero">
            <div class="max-w-3xl">
                <p class="eyebrow text-primary">Kaleb Dunn</p>
                <h1 class="mb-6">I like understanding complicated systems.</h1>
                <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
                    I am interested in the conditions underneath visible results: what gets rewarded, what compounds, what trade-offs get hidden, and
                    what kind of person an environment makes easier to become.
                </p>
            </div>

            <figure class="kaleb-portrait">
                <img src="/images/kaleb-portrait.jpg" alt="Kaleb Dunn" width="1500" height="2250" loading="eager" />
            </figure>
        </section>

        <section class="section-gap grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
            <a href="/kaleb/resume" class="paper-panel no-underline hover:opacity-90">
                <p class="eyebrow text-primary">Resume</p>
                <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl">Work history</h2>
                <p>The practical record: roles, projects, tools, education, and professional background.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/kaleb/thinking" class="paper-panel no-underline hover:opacity-90">
                <p class="eyebrow text-primary">How I Think</p>
                <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl">A working map</h2>
                <p>The organizing ideas: systems, compounding, trade-offs, risk, institutions, and agency.</p>
            </a>

            <div class="paper-panel">
                <p class="eyebrow text-primary">Writing</p>
                <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl">Essays</h2>
                <p>Future pieces on institutions, cities, technology, taste, and the shape of a good life.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="kaleb-closing-note">
            <p class="eyebrow text-primary">Aside</p>
            <p>I am usually trying to understand the structure before I argue about the outcome.</p>
        </section>
    </div>
</Layout>
